{"tid":2058625,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (413）新人開post^^","createTime":"2020-06-10T10:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T10:06:39.000Z","uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"266715c3e27c9eb701ad7c46fcd496870c9c7f58","tid":2058625,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(用依個留言右上角三點可以 「以此內容建立新主題」，用網頁版可以的話copy埋置頂嗰堆，</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">用電話開post置頂內容會爆字數，可以留言叫巴絲幫手post返)</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/528ykNe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F528ykNe.gif&h=442ae26c&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">置頂</span>有實用資訊</strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/528ykNe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F528ykNe.gif&h=442ae26c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xijn341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXijn341.jpg&h=b1337394&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">買game前你可能會想知 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，新增合成元素，你要由零開始<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">還債</span></span></del>建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：去朋友／網友座島度一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">股票</span></span></del><br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係...<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFWQrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFWQrY.png&h=8c46d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">圖片來源 YouTube -&gt; rEB1vlAiVxE</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>代理</strong></span></span>，真係要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得Cloud Save／轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」＆「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好反智</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有近400隻。歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa1FFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=b5dd096f\" target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">特別版主機</span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9736e16150c4c475a18821d4fd06fb1a91c6230d","tid":2058625,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"Ok bye"}]}